## Third-Party Components and Acknowledgments

This project uses the following third-party components:

### dRehmFlight
- **Inspiration**: Control architecture and design patterns
- **Author**: Nicholas Rehm 
- **URL**: https://github.com/nickrehm/dRehmFlight
- **License**: GPL-3.0
- **Note**: No code from dRehmFlight is incorporated in this project. Our PID controllers and flight control algorithms are independent implementations of standard control theory. We acknowledge dRehmFlight as inspiration for the cascaded control architecture design.

### JSBSim
- **License**: LGPL 2.1
- **Description**: Flight dynamics simulation engine
- **Usage**: Used as external dependency for physics validation

### Pybind11
- **License**: BSD-3-Clause
- **Description**: C++/Python binding generator
- **Usage**: Used for C++ integration
